{"tid":1480454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你又話兄弟爬山，而家下下話人係鬼","createTime":"2019-08-17T10:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T11:56:07.000Z","uid":211043,"like":56,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3cbdbf322725ae6678cbfb698fc1dcd69187a0e3","tid":1480454,"uid":211043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:14:11.000Z","msg":"唔同意可以攞出黎傾，講下理據去討論，但唔好下下話「做XXX／圍狗屋／堵路既100%係鬼」。<br />\n<br />\n根本黑警咁高調放啲鬼出黎就係要分化我地，要我地玩捉鬼。<br />\n呢兩個幾月一直都講緊「兄弟爬山，各有各做」，「不分化」。<br />\n呢幾日個個「共識」前「共識」後，根本變相建立緊大台，打壓緊有其他諗法既手足，摒棄左兄弟爬山既原則，咁樣中計玩分化落去，就算前線手足唔比你害死，場運動都遲早收皮。"},{"pid":"eb9d37e830daffa73033d3b3588fea194260daf6","tid":1480454,"uid":211043,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:14:52.000Z","msg":"不分化不割席不篤灰<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做"},{"pid":"87c17dddbddc1d95963bd9fbf8bae464eb0b88f8","tid":1480454,"uid":211043,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:15:21.000Z","msg":"不分化不割席不篤灰<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做"},{"pid":"da67c6948d4c65021295639865d86c062e6dd06b","tid":1480454,"uid":211043,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:15:43.000Z","msg":"推到啲分化撚收皮"},{"pid":"fb36639987ade35c21d2b22cf06686ca53d773d6","tid":1480454,"uid":211043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d074fe4e8705ba7a1c8ee295f5f963d052928c","tid":1480454,"uid":211043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:16:31.000Z","msg":"不分化不割席不篤灰<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做"},{"pid":"071e0454e2c6861fdbe76fe2dac1b155e2011420","tid":1480454,"uid":211043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:17:05.000Z","msg":"推到啲分化撚收皮"},{"pid":"e35e6232bf96029eed5cf946d31569463ebc6618","tid":1480454,"uid":75156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:17:21.000Z","msg":"無錯 點解又綁手綁腳<br />\n如果咁樣既氣氛再重演多一次71 <br />\n我諗應該唔會入到去 大家唔好咁驚"},{"pid":"eb599